，<br />\n留返多D時間互相幫助其他手足會更有意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">其實要贈興，都可以好有技巧：<br />\n佢對武肺呈陽性，<br />\n早就話一有病徵就要求醫，<br />\n佢唔求醫已經係反面教材，<br />\n點知佢呢段時間有冇播毒？<br />\n就算佢住村屋，當佢唔會經喉管播毒，<br />\n但一定有其他緊密接觸者，<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">佢咁樣一樣係累街坊</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd5a27bd3ffec18ec71dc8ae724891d726c23822","tid":2328252,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"呢個就靚抽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羅冠聰：戲子的逝世<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2328184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2328184</a>"},{"pid":"80496c36cae97daa5ac934e804a352b1b9bfcca2","tid":2328252,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5a27bd3ffec18ec71dc8ae724891d726c23822","tid":2328252,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"呢個就靚抽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羅冠聰：戲子的逝世<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2328184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2328184</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"阿聰識諗 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad0f8310fc8eefc274248edf627a77973a37fbf","tid":2328252,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53e991978756e79e9ab2e447faa4c381e20fedc","tid":2328252,"uid":238953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"014d215b2dabaa6aa662a97f1d09b99f82291eed","tid":2328252,"uid":387001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00147d4b780e80a6eceff19eb6246227f22b7045","tid":2328252,"uid":238953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:29:52.000Z","msg":"「有一份尊重」、「都係緣份」<br />\n同經常出嚟搞事嘅藍屍講尊重，講緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTTdVi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTTdVi1.jpg&h=a43f4c